import React from "react";
import { Link } from "react-router-dom";

const CharacterDetail = (props) => {
    console.log(props);
    if (props.character === undefined) {
        return ( <
            div className = "m" >
            <
            div className = "" >
            <
            header className = "" >
            <
            h2 className = "" > No sé Rick, parece falso < /h2> <
            Link to = "/" >
            <
            span className = "icon fas fa-times" > < /span> <
            /Link> <
            /header> <
            section >
            <
            p > x < /p> <
            /section> <
            /div> <
            /div>
        );
    } else {
        return ( <
            div className = "" >
            <
            div className = "" >
            <
            header className = "" >
            <
            h2 className = "" > { props.character.name } < /h2> <
            Link to = "/" >
            <
            span className = "volver" > < /span> <
            /Link> <
            /header> <
            section >
            <
            ul className = "cardsDetail" >
            <
            img className = ""
            src = { props.character.image }
            alt = { `image` + props.character.name }
            /> <
            h4 > { props.character.name } < /h4> <
            h4 > Species: { props.character.species } < /h4> <
            h4 > Planet: { props.character.planet } < /h4> <
            li > Nº episodes: < /li> <
            li > Dead or alive: < /li> <
            /ul> <
            /section> <
            /div> <
            /div>
        );
    }
};

export default CharacterDetail;
